Juanita Quigley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Juanita_Quigley 0 Juanita Quigley (24 June 1931 – 29 October 2017) was an American child actress in motion pictures of the 1930s and 1940s. She had a sister, Rita Quigley, who was also a child actress. Juanita_Quigley ( 24_June_1931 – 29_October_2017 ) was an_American_child_actress in motion_pictures of the_1930s_and_1940s .
